gText_Birch_Welcome::
        .string "Hey! Sorry to keep you waiting!\p"
        .string "Welcome to the region of LAEKON!\p"
        .string "My name is CYPRESS.\p"
        .string "But everyone calls me the POKéMON\n"
        .string "PROFESSOR.\p"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
        .string "This is what we call a POKéMON.\p"
        .string "\n"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
        .string "LAEKON is a land where humans and\n"
        .string "POKéMON have always lived as one.\p"
        .string "Our towns grew where POKéMON\n"
        .string "already were. Our roads bend\l"
        .string "around their homes.\p"
        .string "From that bond was born the\n"
		.string "RANGER CORPS - LAEKON's greatest\l"
        .string "protectors and finest trainers.\p"
        .string "As for me? I study the bond\n"
        .string "itself. What makes a trainer\l"
        .string "and a POKéMON truly partners.\p"
        .string "That question drives everything\n"
        .string "I do.\p"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
        .string "And you are?$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
        .string "Are you a boy?\n"
        .string "Or are you a girl?$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
        .string "All right.\n"
        .string "What's your name?$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
        .string "So it's {PLAYER}{KUN}?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
        .string "Ah, I see!\p"
        .string "You're {PLAYER}{KUN}!\p"
        .string "Today is a big day for you.\p"
        .string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
        .string "The CHALLENGER TOURNAMENT begins\n"
        .string "today.\p"
        .string "Every trainer who dreams of joining\n"
        .string "the RANGER CORPS starts right here.\l"
        .string "Just like you.\p"
        .string "The bond you'll build with your\n"
        .string "POKéMON will be tested at every\l"
        .string "step of the way.\p"
        .string "Are you ready, {PLAYER}{KUN}?\p"
        .string "Your adventure in LAEKON is about\n"
        .string "to begin.\p"
        .string "$"